description: shadcn atoms in packages/ui; modules and organisms in apps/web
globs: apps/web/**
alwaysApply: false
---

# Frontend design system (this monorepo)

- **Atoms (shadcn):** live in `packages/ui/src/components/`. Import from `@workspace/ui/components/<name>` — do not duplicate primitives inside `apps/web` unless intentionally app-only.
- **Modules:** small repeated compositions → `apps/web/components/modules/` (optionally `modules/<feature>/`).
- **Organisms:** page sections / feature blocks → `apps/web/components/organisms/` or colocate under `app/<route>/`.
- **Styling:** Tailwind + tokens in `packages/ui/src/styles/globals.css`; prefer `cn()` from `@workspace/ui/lib/utils` and CSS variables over one-off inline styles.

Adding components: use the shadcn CLI as documented in root `README.md` so files land in `packages/ui`.
